{
  "texts": [
    "These preprocessing steps helped refine the data and enhance the quality of subsequent analysis.",
    "Next, the parsing tree construction phase was conducted.",
    "The Stanford Parser was used in this study to build fully annotated parsing trees, which represent the syntactic structure of the sentences in a hierarchical manner.",
    "The parsing trees provide insights into the relationship between words and phrases, enabling a more in-depth understanding of the textual data.",
    "Upon the parsing tree, the NLTK library (Loper and Bird, 2002) was employed to annotate the parsing tree, enabling understanding of the semantic structure and meaning of the sentences."
  ]
}